  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/zipball/2.2.5",
  "body": "## Updates:\r\n- Synced translations from the [Weblate project](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/zalithlauncher2/)\r\n- Versions: added description for 26w14a (2026 April Fools version HerdCraft)\r\n\r\n## Changes:\r\n- Versions: switched to HMCL tools for version comparison\r\n\r\n## Fixes:\r\n- LWJGL: removed redundant shaderc, by [ShirosakiMio](https://github.com/ShirosakiMio)\r\n- In-game menu: prevented the floating button from moving off-screen when the screen size changes\r\n- Controls: prevented repeated events when long-pressing keyboard buttons",
